name: ListDeploymentsRequest
description:
Request message to list deployments for a project.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.gsuiteaddons.v1.ListDeploymentsRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. Name of the project in which to create the deployment. Example: projects/my_project.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: The maximum number of deployments to return. The service may return fewer than this value. If unspecified, at most 1000 deployments will be returned. The maximum value is 1000; values above 1000 will be coerced to 1000.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: A page token, received from a previous ListDeployments call. Provide this to retrieve the subsequent page. When paginating, all other parameters provided to ListDeployments must match the call that provided the page token.
